placement._description:
The automatic placement string at group level, e. g. web domain, mobile
app ID, or a YouTube channel ID.

target_url._description:
URL of the group placement, e.g. domain, link to the mobile application in
app store, or a YouTube channel URL.

resource_name._description:
The resource name of the group placement view.
Group placement view resource names have the form:


`customers/{customer_id}/groupPlacementViews/{ad_group_id}~{base64_placement}`

_enums.description: Used for return value only. Represents value unknown in this version.

placement_type._description: Type of the placement, e.g. Website, YouTube Channel, Mobile Application.

display_name._description: Domain name for websites and YouTube channel name for YouTube channels.
